nodes.text: Chelpori was a small town on the planet Celen.

In 19 BBY, the Antarian Ranger Jilam Kester and Jedi Master Iri Camas hid there from the Galactic Empire. Kester was eventually discovered and Squad 40 from the 501st Legion was sent to capture him. The squad was distracted by Camas, which allowed Kester to escape.
